OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAustralia gives national   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapology to thalidomide     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsurvivors                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Australia's prime minister has given a 
OL,6, national apology to survivors of the   
OL,7, thalidomide scandal and their families.
OL,9,FIt comes over 60 years after the       
OL,10,Fmorning sickness drug started causing  
OL,11,Fbirth defects in babies globally.      
OL,13,F"This apology takes in one of the      
OL,14,Fdarkest chapters in Australia's medical
OL,15,Fhistory," Anthony Albanese told        
OL,16,Fparliament on Wednesday.               
OL,18,FIt is the first time the government has
OL,19,Facknowledged its role in the tragedy.  
